{"type":"message","id":"ff9bbc85","parentId":"30cc3631","timestamp":"2026-05-11T03:02:35.933Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jo is clarifying - they want to scan 500 Taiwanese stocks using Vegas tunnel criteria. This is about running a screener across ~500 stocks in the Taiwan market. Let me think about what this means and what tools are available.\n\nThe key question is: what exactly do they mean by \"500 stocks\"? In Taiwan, the main indices cover:\n- Taiwan 50 (top 50)\n- Taiwan 100\n- Mid 100 / Mid 100 II\n- The broader market has many more stocks\n\n\"500檔\" likely refers to scanning a broad universe - either the Top 500 by market cap, or perhaps a specific known list. \n\nSince they didn't specify a particular product or service, they probably want to know what tools can actually handle scanning this many stocks with custom technical criteria like Vegas tunnel indicators. The practical options are CMoney's stock screener which can filter by custom technical conditions, XQ's quantitative module for writing custom scripts, or TradingView which supports custom indicator scans across multiple securities.\n\nGiven Taiwan's stock market structure, a scan of 500 stocks would likely use the Taiwan 500 by market cap or the broader listed stock universe. I should focus on what tools are actually available and practical for this kind of bulk technical screening rather than guessing at specific products they might have seen.","thinkingSignature":"25d610cde0ed45314d408ac152d479de11bf1ac973fc984a74f572f018fd8eb2"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n\n了解，就是想要**用 Vegas 隧道邏輯對台股約 500 檔股票進行技術面掃描**。\n\n---\n\n## 📊 實務上怎麼做\n\n台股 500 檔通常指**市值排名前 500 的上市股票**（涵蓋台灣 50、100、中型 100 到整體市場的核心）。\n\n### 推薦工具\n\n| 平台 | 能否掃 500 檔 | 能否自訂 Vegas 條件 |\n|------|:---:|:---:|\n| **CMoney 選股** | ✅ 可 | ⚠️ 需搭配其 App（技術面條件） |\n| **XQ 全球贏家** | ✅ 可 | ✅ 自寫選股腳本（XS 語法） |\n| **玩股網** | ✅ 可 | ⚠️ 預設條件為主 |\n| **TradingView** | ✅ 可（台股有資料） | ✅ 可自寫指標 |\n| **Finage / 其它券商 API** | ✅ 可 | ✅ 自訂篩選 |\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 我可以幫你什麼\n\n如果你想**實際跑起來**，有幾個方向：\n\n**方向 1：用 XQ 寫 Vegas 選股腳本**\n- XQ 有 SDK 可以寫 XS（選股腳本）\n- 寫一個「價格 + EMA12 突破 EMA144/169 隧道」的多頭篩選器\n- 掛在 500 檔上跑每天掃描\n- **我可以幫你寫 XS 選股腳本** 🚀\n\n**方向 2：用 TradingView**\n- Pine Script 寫 Vegas 指標 + screener\n- TradingView 的台股資料覆蓋度還行\n- 缺點：国台股資料深度不如專業台股軟體\n\n**方向 3：用 Python + 資料庫**\n- 用 twstock / FinMind 等取得台股資料\n- 自己算 EMA144/169/576/676\n- Pandas 跑全市場篩選\n- **我可以幫你寫 Python 腳本** 🚀\n\n---\n\n你想要往哪個方向走？我來幫你實作。📈"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":106,"output":727,"cacheRead":9845,"cacheWrite":33331,"totalTokens":44009,"cost":{"input":0.0000318,"output":0.0008724,"cacheRead":0.0005907,"cacheWrite":0.012499125,"total":0.013994025}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778468518512,"responseId":"065079a94d8ffb17ba4aadc9ae3992c4"}}
