{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:1616824689\",\n  \"message_id\": \"1426\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1616824689\",\n  \"sender\": \"Jo\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-05-11 11:02 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Jo (1616824689)\",\n  \"id\": \"1616824689\",\n  \"name\": \"Jo\",\n  \"username\": \"jojo_naan\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"c4b20ba4","parentId":"de7f7e05","timestamp":"2026-05-11T03:02:45.366Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"89c688af","parentId":"c4b20ba4","timestamp":"2026-05-11T03:03:36.856Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jo chose direction A - using XQ to write a Vegas stock screening script. Let me write an XS (XQ) selection script for the Vegas tunnel strategy.\n\nThe Vegas tunnel logic for long (做多):\n1. Price + EMA12 simultaneously break above the tunnel (EMA144 + EMA169)\n2. Price is above EMA576 and EMA676 (big trend is up)\n3. Filter: when price breaks tunnel but EMA12 doesn't confirm, it's a false signal\n\nFor screening 500 stocks, I need to write an XQ/XS script that:\n- Uses EMA(close, 12), EMA(close, 144), EMA(close, 169), EMA(close, 576), EMA(close, 676)\n\n\n- Checks for golden cross conditions where short-term EMAs are rising\n- Validates that price momentum aligns with the broader trend confirmation from the longer EMAs\n\nNow I'll write the actual XS code to implement these conditions.","thinkingSignature":"2781bba941011bb9e44d8d5e38a45db5fcfb055d3129a42dd148fc4bb6d219c0"},{"type":"text","text":"\n好，幫你寫 XQ 選股腳本。📈\n\n---\n\n## Vegas 隧道選股腳本（XQ / XS 語法）\n\n```xs\n// Vegas Tunnel 多頭篩選器\n// 適用：台股上市櫃個股 (可設 500 檔)\n\n// ========== 參數設定 ==========\ninput: EMA12_Period(12, \"EMA12 過濾線\");\ninput: EMA144_Period(144, \"隧道上軌\");\ninput: EMA169_Period(169, \"隧道下軌\");\ninput: EMA576_Period(576, \"大趨勢線1\");\ninput: EMA676_Period(676, \"大趨勢線2\");\n\n// ========== 計算 EMA ==========\nvar: ema12(0), ema144(0), ema169(0), ema576(0), ema676(0);\nema12 = XAverage(close, EMA12_Period);\nema144 = XAverage(close, EMA144_Period);\nema169 = XAverage(close, EMA169_Period);\nema576 = XAverage(close, EMA576_Period);\nema676 = XAverage(close, EMA676_Period);\n\n// ========== 隧道狀態 ==========\n// 隧道是否多頭排列 (144 > 169 且向上)\nvar: tunnel_bull(false);\ntunnel_bull = ema144 > ema169 and ema144 > ema144[1] and ema169 > ema169[1];\n\n// 大趨勢是否多頭 (价格在 576/676 之上，且 576 > 676)\nvar: bigtrend_bull(false);\nbigtrend_bull = close > ema576 and close > ema676 \n                and ema576 > ema676 and ema576 > ema576[1] and ema676 > ema676[1];\n\n// ========== 突破訊號 ==========\n// 條件1：價格向上突破隧道 (今收 > ema144 且 昨收 <= ema169 或 昨收 <= ema144)\nvar: price_breakout(false);\nprice_breakout = close > ema144 and close > ema169\n                 and (close[1] <= ema144[1] or close[1] <= ema169[1]);\n\n// 條件2：EMA12 同步確認突破 (今 > ema144 且 昨 <= ema144)\nvar: ema12_confirm(false);\nema12_confirm = ema12 > ema144 and ema12 > ema169\n                and ema12[1] <= ema144[1];\n\n// ========== 過濾假突破 ==========\n// 過濾條件：價格突破但 EMA12 未確認 → 排除\nvar: false_breakout(false);\nfalse_breakout = price_breakout and not ema12_confirm;\n\n// ========== 進場訊號 ==========\n// 同時滿足：隧道多頭 + 大趨勢多頭 + 真突破\nvar: signal_long(false);\nsignal_long = tunnel_bull and bigtrend_bull \n              and price_breakout and ema12_confirm\n              and not false_breakout;\n\n// ========== 額外過濾（可選） ==========\n// 成交量放大 > 前一日 1.5 倍\nvar: vol_spike(false);\nvol_spike = volume > volume[1] * 1.5;\n\n// RSI 過濾（避免追高 RSI > 85）\nvar: rsi_val(0);\nrsi_val = RSI(close, 14);\nvar: rsi_filter(false);\nrsi_filter = rsi_val < 85;\n\n// ========== 輸出 ==========\n// 多頭條件滿足\nif signal_long and rsi_filter then begin\n    Output.Add(Condition = True, PlotNumber = 0, Icon = 1);\n    // OutputField: 自訂顯示欄位\n    OutputField.SetText(\"Vegas多頭突破\");\nend;\n\n// ========== 進階：強度評分（可選） ==========\n// 多頭排列強度：計算均線之間的差距\nvar: tunnel_width(0), trend_width(0);\ntunnel_width = (ema144 - ema169) / ema169 * 100;  // 隧道寬度 %\ntrend_width  = (ema576 - ema676) / ema676 * 100;  // 大趨勢寬度 %\n\n// 評分輸出\nOutputField1.SetValue(tunnel_width, \"隧道寬度%\");\nOutputField2.SetValue(trend_width,  \"大趨勢寬度%\");\nOutputField3.SetValue(rsi_val,       \"RSI(14)\");\nOutputField4.SetValue(vol,            \"成交量\");\n```\n\n---\n\n## 在 XQ 中設定方式\n\n**步驟：**\n1. 打開 XQ → **選股中心** → **新增策略**\n2. 選擇「** XS 選股腳本**」\n3. 命名例如：`Vegas_隧道_多頭_500檔`\n4. 貼上上方腳本\n5. **選擇標的**：點「設定」→ 勾選「**自選股群組**」→ 匯入市值前 500 檔（TWSE 500）\n6. **執行頻率**：每天盤後或盤中定期掃描\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 提醒\n\n- **EMA576 / EMA676** 在日線上算是很長的週期，有些體質不佳的個股可能根本跑不出資料，必要時可降到 `EMA144 / EMA169 / EMA288`（144×2）代替\n- 如果你想更保守，可再多加一個條件：**法人連續買超 N 日**\n- RSI > 85 進場容易追高，可以改成 < 80 更穩健\n\n---\n\n需要我幫你：\n1. **簡化版本**（只看隧道突破，減少參數）？\n2. **寫 Python 版本**（串 FinMind / twstock，全市場自己跑）？\n3. **幫你匯出市值前 500 檔的股票清單**？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":106,"output":1515,"cacheRead":43045,"cacheWrite":602,"totalTokens":45268,"cost":{"input":0.0000318,"output":0.001818,"cacheRead":0.0025827,"cacheWrite":0.00022575,"total":0.00465825}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778468565366,"responseId":"065079d8c85e0b47b2dbb8fbaf238d93"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9a796902","parentId":"89c688af","timestamp":"2026-05-11T04:44:16.283Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. 串yfinance 或永豐api\nReply target of current user message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Ray\",\n  \"body\": \"好，幫你寫 XQ 選股腳本。📈\\n\\n───\\n\\nVegas 隧道選股腳本（XQ / XS 語法）\\n\\n// Vegas Tunnel 多頭篩選器\\n// 適用：台股上市櫃個股 (可設 500 檔)\\n\\n// ========== 參數設定 ==========\\ninput: EMA12_Period(12, \\\"EMA12 過濾線\\\");\\ninput: EMA144_Period(144, \\\"隧道上軌\\\");\\ninput: EMA169_Period(169, \\\"隧道下軌\\\");\\ninput: EMA576_Period(576, \\\"大趨勢線1\\\");\\ninput: EMA676_Period(676, \\\"大趨勢線2\\\");\\n\\n// ========== 計算 EMA ==========\\nvar: ema12(0), ema144(0), ema169(0), ema576(0), ema676(0);\\nema12 = XAverage(close, EMA12_Period);\\nema144 = XAverage(close, EMA144_Period);\\nema169 = XAverage(close, EMA169_Period);\\nema576 = XAverage(close, EMA576_Period);\\nema676 = XAverage(close, EMA676_Period);\\n\\n// ========== 隧道狀態 ==========\\n// 隧道是否多頭排列 (144 > 169 且向上)\\nvar: tunnel_bull(false);\\ntunnel_bull = ema144 > ema169 and ema144 > ema144[1] and ema169 > ema169[1];\\n\\n// 大趨勢是否多頭 (价格在 576/676 之上，且 576 > 676)\\nvar: bigtrend_bull(false);\\nbigtrend_bull = close > ema576 and close > ema676 \\n                and ema576 > ema676 and ema576 > ema576[1] and ema676 > ema676[1];\\n\\n// ========== 突破訊號 ==========\\n// 條件1：價格向上突破隧道 (今收 > ema144 且 昨收 <= ema169 或 昨收 <= ema144)\\nvar: price_breakout(false);\\nprice_breakout = close > ema144 and close > ema169\\n                 and (close[1] <= ema144[1] or close[1] <= ema169[1]);\\n\\n// 條件2：EMA12 同步確認突破 (今 > ema144 且 昨 <= ema144)\\nvar: ema12_confirm(false);\\nema12_confirm = ema12 > ema144 and ema12 > ema169\\n                and ema12[1] <= ema144[1];\\n\\n// ========== 過濾假突破 ==========\\n// 過濾條件：價格突破但 EMA12 未確認 → 排除\\nvar: false_breakout(false);\\nfalse_breakout = price_breakout and not ema12_confirm;\\n\\n// ========== 進場訊號 ==========\\n// 同時滿足：隧道多頭 + 大趨勢多頭 + 真突破\\nvar: signal_long(false);\\nsignal_long = tunnel_bull and bigtrend_bull \\n              and price_breakout and ema12_confirm\\n              and not false_breakout;\\n\\n// ========== 額外過濾（可選） ==========\\n// 成交量放大 > 前一日 1.5 倍\\nvar: vol_spike(false);\\nvol_spike = volume > volume[1] * 1.5;\\n\\n// RSI 過濾（避免追高 RSI > 85）\\nvar: rsi_val(0);\\nrsi_val = RSI(close, 14);\\nvar: rsi_filter(false);\\nrsi_filter = rsi_val < 85;\\n\\n// ==========…[truncated]\"\n}\n```"}],"timestamp":1778474656282}}
