{"type":"message","id":"a9f6b5da","parentId":"11fd9882","timestamp":"2026-05-11T05:18:45.498Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jo chose Shioaji (永豐金). Now I need to write a Python script that:\n1. Uses Shioaji to connect to 永豐金 API\n2. Gets a list of Taiwan stocks (approximately 500 stocks - likely the top 500 by market cap)\n3. Implements the Vegas Tunnel logic for scanning\n4. Outputs results when manually run (not scheduled)\n\nLet me write a comprehensive Python script using Shioaji. The script should:\n- Connect to Shioaji\n- Fetch list of stocks (likely from TWSE or using a curated list)\n- Calculate EMA12, EMA144, EMA169, EMA576, EMA676\n\n\n- Detect breakout signals and provide scan results\n\nI need to be careful with Shioaji installation and configuration since it requires a Shioaji account with 永豐金. Now I'm writing the main scanning script that handles the connection and implements the Vegas Tunnel strategy.\n\nThe script will calculate exponential moving averages across multiple periods, then identify when the tunnel formed by EMA144 and EMA169 aligns with the broader trend from EMA576 and EMA676. It detects genuine breakouts by checking if price and EMA12 both cross above the tunnel while filtering out false signals.\n\nWriting the scan function...\n\nFor Taiwan stocks, I'll fetch the top 500 by market cap from TWSE, though Shioaji doesn't have a direct method for this so I might need to either use a pre-defined list or pull from the Taiwan Stock Exchange API. I'm planning to generate the complete Python script now, starting with the necessary imports and setup for the Shioaji library and EMA calculations, then building out the stock scanning and signal detection logic.\n\nFor the stock universe, I should work with a curated list of Taiwan's top 500 stocks rather than trying to dynamically fetch them, since that's more reliable and accessible. I'll include guidance on how to customize this list based on market cap or other criteria.\n\nWriting the complete script...\n","thinkingSignature":"83faf813b34a1e627c43202ef28ffca740a2d553eb9d45e09599fc00e543c57a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，寫一個完整的 `vegas_scan.py`，串 Shioaji（永豐金 API），隨選執行。📈\n\n先把腳本寫好，你再去裝相關套件和設定。開始：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fx7wx817f4xi_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nVegas Tunnel 掃描器 - Shioaji 版\n用途：隨選掃描台股 500 檔，找出 Vegas 多頭突破訊號\n使用：python vegas_scan.py\n依賴：pip install shioaji pandas ta\n\"\"\"\n\nimport shioaji as sj\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nimport warnings\nwarnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n\n# ========================\n# 參數設定\n# ========================\n# Shioaji 登入（請替換成你的 FUGLE API KEY）\nAPI_KEY = \"YOUR_API_KEY\"\nAPI_SECRET = \"YOUR_API_SECRET\"\n\n# 股票池：市值前 500 檔（已包含常見標的，可自行擴充）\n# 可從 twstock 或 TWSE 取得完整列表後替換\nTSE_TOP500 = [\n    \"2330\", \"2317\", \"2454\", \"2382\", \"2376\", \"2377\", \"2395\", \"2408\", \"2451\",\n    \"2303\", \"2308\", \"2357\", \"2360\", \"2379\", \"2380\", \"2399\", \"2449\", \"2468\",\n    \"2472\", \"2478\", \"2492\", \"2723\", \"2727\", \"2734\", \"3034\", \"3036\", \"3037\",\n    \"3231\", \"3443\", \"3504\", \"3530\", \"3545\", \"3570\", \"3583\", \"3587\", \"3661\",\n    \"3682\", \"3702\", \"3704\", \"3711\", \"3712\", \"4174\", \"4426\", \"4743\", \"4763\",\n    \"4919\", \"4952\", \"4958\", \"5225\", \"5264\", \"5347\", \"5426\", \"5522\", \"5871\",\n    \"5880\", \"6024\", \"6104\", \"6116\", \"6120\", \"6176\", \"6180\", \"6191\", \"6214\",\n    \"6239\", \"6251\", \"6253\", \"6269\", \"6271\", \"6409\", \"6415\", \"6443\", \"6454\",\n    \"6552\", \"6556\", \"6568\", \"6573\", \"6579\", \"6589\", \"6592\", \"6625\", \"6655\",\n    \"6669\", \"6670\", \"6683\", \"6706\", \"6741\", \"6770\", \"8016\", \"8028\", \"8033\",\n    \"8046\", \"8081\", \"8097\", \"8104\", \"8114\", \"8261\", \"8358\", \"8367\", \"8454\",\n    \"8464\", \"8481\", \"8926\", \"8996\", \"9802\", \"9810\", \"9933\", \"9958\",\n    # 以上為部分代表性個股，完整 500 檔請參考 get_top500_stocks() 或從 twstock 取得\n]\n\n# 完整列表見本檔案最後，或使用 twstock 動態抓取\n# 為求腳本可獨立運行，請運行一次 python vegas_scan.py --fetch-list 先抓完整列表\n\n# ========================\n# 工具函式：計算 EMA\n# ========================\ndef calc_ema(series: pd.Series, period: int) -> pd.Series:\n    \"\"\"計算指數移動平均線\"\"\"\n    return series.ewm(span=period, adjust=False).mean()\n\n# ========================\n# 工具函式：Vegas 信號計算\n# ========================\ndef vegas_signal(df: pd.DataFrame):\n    \"\"\"\n    根據 Vegas 隧道邏輯計算多頭/空頭/無訊號\n    返回 dict {\n        'trend': 'BULL' / 'BEAR' / 'NEUTRAL',\n        'ema12': float, 'ema144': float, 'ema169': float,\n        'ema576': float, 'ema676': float,\n        'tunnel_width': float,   # 隧道寬度 %\n        'trend_width': float,    # 大趨勢寬度 %\n        'breakout': bool,\n        'rsi14': float,\n        'score': int             # 1-5 分強度評分\n    }\n    \"\"\"\n    close = df['close']\n    open_ = df['open']\n    high = df['high']\n    low = df['low']\n    volume = df['volume']\n\n    # 計算五條 EMA\n    ema12  = calc_ema(close, 12)\n    ema144 = calc_ema(close, 144)\n    ema169 = calc_ema(close, 169)\n    ema576 = calc_ema(close, 576)\n    ema676 = calc_ema(close, 676)\n\n    # 取最新值（最後一根 K 棒）\n    e12  = ema12.iloc[-1]\n    e144 = ema144.iloc[-1]\n    e169 = ema169.iloc[-1]\n    e576 = ema576.iloc[-1]\n    e676 = ema676.iloc[-1]\n    c    = close.iloc[-1]\n    c1   = close.iloc[-2] if len(close) > 1 else c\n    e12_1 = ema12.iloc[-2] if len(ema12) > 1 else e12\n    e144_1= ema144.iloc[-2] if len(ema144) > 1 else e144\n\n    # ---- 隧道狀態 ----\n    tunnel_bull   = (e144 > e169) and (e144 > ema144.iloc[-2]) and (e169 > ema169.iloc[-2])\n    tunnel_bear   = (e144 < e169) and (e144 < ema144.iloc[-2]) and (e169 < ema169.iloc[-2])\n\n    # ---- 大趨勢狀態 ----\n    bigtrend_bull = (c > e576) and (c > e676) and (e576 > e676) and (e576 > ema576.iloc[-2])\n    bigtrend_bear = (c < e576) and (c < e676) and (e576 < e676) and (e576 < ema576.iloc[-2])\n\n    # ---- 突破訊號 ----\n    # 價格向上突破隧道：今收 > 隧道上軌，且昨日低於隧道\n    price_breakout_up   = (c > e144) and (c > e169) and (c1 <= e144)\n    # EMA12 同步確認突破\n    ema12_confirm_up    = (e12 > e144) and (e12 > e169) and (e12_1 <= e144)\n    # 假突破：價格突破但 EMA12 未確認\n    false_breakout_up   = price_breakout_up and not ema12_confirm_up\n\n    # ---- RSI(14) ----\n    delta = close.diff()\n    gain = delta.clip(lower=0).ewm(alpha=1/14, adjust=False).mean()\n    loss = (-delta.clip(upper=0)).ewm(alpha=1/14, adjust=False).mean()\n    rs = gain / loss\n    rsi14 = 100 - (100 / (1 + rs))\n    rsi_val = rsi14.iloc[-1] if not rsi14.empty else 50\n\n    # ---- 評分 ----\n    score = 0\n    if tunnel_bull:   score += 1\n    if bigtrend_bull: score += 1\n    if price_breakout_up and ema12_confirm_up and not false_breakout_up: score += 2\n    if rsi_val < 80:  score += 1   # RSI 未過熱 +1\n    score = min(score, 5)\n\n    # ---- 隧道寬度 ----\n    tunnel_width = (e144 - e169) / e169 * 100 if e169 != 0 else 0\n    trend_width  = (e576 - e676) / e676 * 100 if e676 != 0 else 0\n\n    # ---- 判斷趨勢 ----\n    if price_breakout_up and ema12_confirm_up and tunnel_bull and bigtrend_bull and not false_breakout_up:\n        trend = 'BULL'\n        breakout = True\n    elif tunnel_bull and bigtrend_bull:\n        trend = 'BULL_LAGGING'  # 多頭但尚未突破\n        breakout = False\n    elif tunnel_bear and bigtrend_bear:\n        trend = 'BEAR'\n        breakout = False\n    else:\n        trend = 'NEUTRAL'\n        breakout = False\n\n    return {\n        'trend': trend,\n        'ema12': round(e12, 2),\n        'ema144': round(e144, 2),\n        'ema169': round(e169, 2),\n        'ema576': round(e576, 2),\n        'ema676': round(e676, 2),\n        'tunnel_width': round(tunnel_width, 3),\n        'trend_width': round(trend_width, 3),\n        'breakout': breakout,\n        'rsi14': round(rsi_val, 1),\n        'score': score,\n        'close': round(c, 2),\n        'volume': int(volume.iloc[-1]),\n    }\n\n# ========================\n# Shioaji 登入與取得報價\n# ========================\ndef login_shioaji():\n    \"\"\"連接 Shioaji（永豐金）\"\"\"\n    api = sj.Shioaji()\n    api.login(\n        api_key=API_KEY,\n        api_secret=API_SECRET,\n        contracts_timeout=30000,\n        subscribe_timeout=30000,\n    )\n    print(f\"✅ Shioaji 登入成功 | 版本: {sj.__version__}\")\n    return api\n\ndef get_kbar(api, stock_code: str, days: int = 300):\n    \"\"\"\n    取得個股 K 棒資料（使用歷史 K 棒）\n    days: 回溯天數（預設 300 天，確保 EMA576 有足夠資料）\n    \"\"\"\n    contract = api.Contracts.Stocks[stock_code]\n    if contract is None:\n        return None\n\n    end_date = datetime.today()\n    start_date = end_date - timedelta(days=days)\n\n    try:\n        kbars = api.kbars(\n            contract=contract,\n            start=start_date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d'),\n            end=end_date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d'),\n        )\n        df = pd.DataFrame(kbars)\n        df['date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['ts'], unit='s')\n        df = df.rename(columns={\n            'Open': 'open', 'High': 'high',\n            'Low': 'low', 'Close': 'close', 'Volume': 'volume'\n        })\n        df = df[['date', 'open', 'high', 'low', 'close', 'volume']].drop_duplicates('date')\n        df = df.sort_values('date').reset_index(drop=True)\n        return df\n    except Exception as e:\n        return None\n\n# ========================\n# 主掃描程序\n# ========================\ndef scan_vegas(api, stock_list: list, min_score: int = 3):\n    \"\"\"\n    掃描股票池，回傳符合條件的標的\n    min_score: 最低評分門檻（預設 3 分以上）\n    \"\"\"\n    results = []\n    total = len(stock_list)\n    count = 0\n\n    print(f\"\\n🚀 Vegas 隧道掃描開始 | 目標: {total} 檔 | 最低評分: {min_score}\")\n    print(\"=\" * 60)\n\n    for code in stock_list:\n        count += 1\n        # 每 50 檔印一次進度\n        if count % 50 == 0 or count == total:\n            print(f\"  掃描進度: {count}/{total} ({count*100//total}%)\")\n\n        df = get_kbar(api, code, days=350)\n        if df is None or len(df) < 200:\n            continue  # 資料不足（EMA576 需要夠長）\n\n        try:\n            sig = vegas_signal(df)\n        except Exception:\n            continue\n\n        if sig['score'] >= min_score:\n            sig['code'] = code\n            sig['name'] = get_stock_name(api, code)\n            results.append(sig)\n\n    # 排序：分數高的在前，突破訊號優先\n    results.sort(key=lambda x: (x['score'], x['breakout']), reverse=True)\n\n    return results\n\ndef get_stock_name(api, code: str) -> str:\n    \"\"\"取得股票名稱\"\"\"\n    try:\n        contract = api.Contracts.Stocks[code]\n        return contract.name if contract else code\n    except:\n        return code\n\ndef print_results(results: list):\n    \"\"\"格式化輸出結果\"\"\"\n    if not results:\n        print(\"\\n❌ 沒有找到符合條件的標的\")\n        return\n\n    print(f\"\\n✅ 找到 {len(results)} 檔符合 Vegas 多頭條件:\")\n    print(\"=\" * 80)\n    print(f\"{'代碼':<8}{'名稱':<12}{'評分':<6}{'現價':<10}{'EMA12':<10}{'隧道上軌':<10}{'隧道下軌':<10}{'RSI':<8}{'突破'}\")\n    print(\"-\" * 80)\n\n    for r in results:\n        breakout_tag = \"🚀\" if r['breakout'] else \"  \"\n        print(\n            f\"{r['code']:<8}\"\n            f\"{r['name']:<12}\"\n            f\"{r['score']:<6}\"\n            f\"{r['close']:<10.2f}\"\n            f\"{r['ema12']:<10.2f}\"\n            f\"{r['ema144']:<10.2f}\"\n            f\"{r['ema169']:<10.2f}\"\n            f\"{r['rsi14']:<8.1f}\"\n            f\"{breakout_tag}\"\n        )\n\n    # 突破訊號另外列出\n    breakouts = [r for r in results if r['breakout']]\n    if breakouts:\n        print(\"\\n\" + \"🔥\" * 20)\n        print(f\"🚨 突破訊號 ({len(breakouts)} 檔)\")\n        print(\"=\" * 80)\n        for r in breakouts:\n            print(f\"  🚀 {r['code']} {r['name']} | 現價:{r['close']} | EMA12:{r['ema12']} | 隧道:{r['ema144']:.2f}-{r['ema169']:.2f} | RSI:{r['rsi14']} | 評分:{r['score']}/5\")\n\n# ========================\n# 工具：TWSE 前 500 檔（可自動更新）\n# ========================\ndef fetch_top500_from_twse():\n    \"\"\"\n    從台灣證交所取得上市股票清單（依市值排序）\n    需 pip install requests\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        import requests\n        # TWSE 歷史 New取代 證券界面API\n        url = \"https://www.twse.com.tw/rwd/zh/afterTrading/MI_INDEX?type=ALL&date=&code=&ajax=true\"\n        # 此處擷取方式可能需更新，請以實際 TWSE 頁面為準\n        print(\"⚠️  TWSE 完整列表擷取需要額外處理，建議使用靜態列表或 twstock 套件\")\n        return TSE_TOP500\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"⚠️  無法取得 TWSE 清單，使用預設列表: {e}\")\n        return TSE_TOP500\n\n# ========================\n# 主程式\n# ========================\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    import sys\n\n    if \"--fetch-list\" in sys.argv:\n        # 僅抓取股票清單，不執行掃描\n        stocks = fetch_top500_from_twse()\n        print(f\"股票清單共 {len(stocks)} 檔\")\n        for s in stocks:\n            print(s)\n        sys.exit(0)\n\n    print(\"=\" * 60)\n    print(\"📈 Vegas 隧道掃描器 | Shioaji 版 | 隨選執行\")\n    print(f\"時間: {datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}\")\n    print(\"=\" * 60)\n\n    # 登入 Shioaji\n    try:\n        api = login_shioaji()\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ Shioaji 登入失敗: {e}\")\n        print(\"請確認 API_KEY / API_SECRET 是否正確\")\n        print(\"或至 https://sinotrade.github.io/shioaji/ 申請\")\n        sys.exit(1)\n\n    # 取得股票清單（可替換為 fetch_top500_from_twse() 動態抓取）\n    stock_list = TSE_TOP500\n    print(f\"📋 股票池: {len(stock_list)} 檔\")\n\n    # 執行掃描（評分門檻可調，預設 3 分）\n    results = scan_vegas(api, stock_list, min_score=3)\n\n    # 輸出結果\n    print_results(results)\n\n    # 存檔\n    if results:\n        save_results(results)\n        print(f\"\\n💾 結果已儲存至 vegas_results_{datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d_%H%M%S')}.csv\")\n\n    print(\"\\n✅ 掃描完成\")\n\ndef save_results(results: list):\n    \"\"\"將結果存成 CSV\"\"\"\n    df = pd.DataFrame(results)\n    ts = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d_%H%M%S')\n    filename = f\"vegas_results_{ts}.csv\"\n    df.to_csv(filename, index=False, encoding='utf-8-sig')\n    print(f\"💾 儲存: {filename}\")","path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\vegas_scan.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":637,"output":4415,"cacheRead":46144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51196,"cost":{"input":0.00019109999999999998,"output":0.005298,"cacheRead":0.0027686399999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00825774}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778476595865,"responseId":"06509935d739f31a4af82305e6a01806"}}
