{"type":"message","id":"8170dd15","parentId":"1e6cc92c","timestamp":"2026-05-11T05:19:03.550Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the file was written. Now let me explain what I did and how to use it.\n","thinkingSignature":"4e5dbf1d1405afccfe8534ee374f6f71d5872d3e5799432b5f317f7b5dfba5e7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n已寫入 `vegas_scan.py` 📈\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 使用方式\n\n**1. 安裝依賴**\n```bash\npip install shioaji pandas ta\n```\n\n**2. 填入你的永豐金 API Key**\n打開 `vegas_scan.py`，找到這行，替換成你的：\n```python\nAPI_KEY = \"***\"\nAPI_SECRET = \"***\"\n```\n（申請：永豐金 `Shioaji` → https://sinotrade.github.io/shioaji/）\n\n**3. 執行**\n```bash\npython vegas_scan.py\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📊 掃描邏輯\n\n| 評分項目 | 分數 |\n|---------|------|\n| 隧道多頭（EMA144 > EMA169 且向上） | +1 |\n| 大趨勢多頭（價格 > EMA576/676 且多頭排列） | +1 |\n| **真突破**（價格 + EMA12 同時突破隧道） | +2 |\n| RSI < 80（未過熱） | +1 |\n| **滿分** | **5 分** |\n\n預設門檻 `min_score=3`，想嚴格一點改成 `4`。\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 注意\n\n- **股票池**我放了部分代表性個股（約 100 檔），500 檔完整版需要從 TWSE 或 CMoney 抓取完整列表（可跑一次 `python vegas_scan.py --fetch-list`）\n- **EMA576 需要 300 天的資料**，所以會自動跳過上市不滿一年的股票\n- 第一次執行因為要登入 + 下載 K 棒，會慢一些（50 檔約 30-60 秒）\n\n---\n\n需要我：\n1. **補齊完整的 500 檔股票清單**？\n2. **改成 `yfinance` 版本**（不用 API key，國外券商）？\n3. **加進 FinMind API**（無需帳戶，開源抓台股）？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4072,"output":452,"cacheRead":46720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51244,"cost":{"input":0.0012216,"output":0.0005424,"cacheRead":0.0028031999999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0045671999999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778476725617,"responseId":"065099b6370caa4689d1359a81fef53d"}}
