{"type":"message","id":"1988a234","parentId":"6ce95a93","timestamp":"2026-05-11T09:22:34.374Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, so we have 107 stock codes in the list. Jo is asking about the scan scope (範圍). Currently it's only 107 stocks, not 500. I should tell him the current state and offer to generate the full 500.\n\nLet me reply to Jo about the current scope status.\n","thinkingSignature":"f701541418ceeaf37298def09c93d2e7646e6c7c2b59ad60c6f08984e1eb6424"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n目前 `vegas_scan.py` 的股票池只有 **107 檔**示範清單，不是 500 檔完整版。\n\n---\n\n## 📊 現況\n\n| 項目 | 內容 |\n|------|------|\n| 目標 | 500 檔（市值排名前 500 的上市櫃） |\n| 現況 | 只有 107 檔示範用 |\n| 原因 | 完整 500 檔需要另外補上 |\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 要補齊嗎？\n\n我可以幫你：\n1. **自動抓 TWSE 完整上市股票清單**，補到 500 檔以上\n2. **手動補常見的 500 檔列表**\n\n只要告訴我，我現在就更新 `vegas_scan.py`，把股票池擴充完整。\n\n另外，**Shioaji 的 Key 還沒認證成功**（`key not exist`），更新完股票清單之後要確認一下登入方式是否正確，才能執行掃描。\n\n要我現在補完整股票清單嗎？📈"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":235,"output":283,"cacheRead":58752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59270,"cost":{"input":0.00007049999999999999,"output":0.00033959999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0035251199999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00393522}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778491331832,"responseId":"0650d2c4bf9f9985f3b50e86b99ec1bd"}}
