{"type":"message","id":"ff8a84ed","parentId":"8a7ddde4","timestamp":"2026-05-11T09:38:40.740Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The TWSE API returns index data, not individual stock data. I need a different approach to get the stock list. Let me try the listed company API or just use a static list approach with a fetch fallback.\n\nActually, for this use case, the cleanest approach is:\n1. Use a hardcoded list of major TWSE stocks (the top 500 codes are well-known)\n2. For US stocks, use yfinance ticker download\n\nOr I can use a different source - let me check if there's a reliable CSV or JSON endpoint for TWSE stock list.\n\nActually, let me simplify this. Given the complexity of getting a perfect TWSE list, let me just:\n\n\n1. Build a comprehensive static TWSE list from memory with the major stocks\n2. Pull S&P500 and NASDAQ-100 from Wikipedia dynamically\n3. Use a static list for SOX30\n4. For getting fresh TWSE data, try the Shioaji contracts approach instead\n\nBut really, I should just write this as a comprehensive Python file. Let me save it directly since the write tool keeps truncating through the exec channel.\n","thinkingSignature":"81eca85cd5fe71bd71821ef16ee8c8bb4e9da495b1c6212a83a0a8eeaf2ad2d5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_iytkyv3et3x2_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nVegas Tunnel 掃描器 - 全市場版\n台股 TWSE 500: FinMind(優先) / yfinance(備用)\n美股 S&P500 / NASDAQ100 / SOX30: yfinance(即時)\n\n執行: python vegas_scan.py\n\"\"\"\n\nimport sys, os\nsys.path.insert(0, r'C:\\Users\\USER\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python312\\Lib\\site-packages')\nsys.path.insert(0, os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(__file__)))\n\nimport yfinance as yf\nfrom FinMind.data import DataLoader\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nimport warnings, ssl, json, urllib.request\nwarnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n\n# ========================\n# 參數\n# ========================\nMIN_SCORE = 3\nBACKTEST_DAYS = 700\n\n# ========================\n# 工具：fetch TWSE 股票清單\n# ========================\ndef fetch_twse_list():\n    \"\"\"從 TWSE API 取得上市股票代碼\"\"\"\n    ctx = ssl.create_default_context()\n    ctx.check_hostname = False\n    ctx.verify_mode = ssl.CERT_NONE\n    headers = {'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0', 'Accept': 'application/json'}\n\n    # 嘗試多个端點\n    urls = [\n        'https://www.twse.com.tw/rwd/zh/afterTrading/MI_INDEX?date=&type=ALL&response=json',\n        'https://www.twse.com.tw/rwd/zh/listed/search_result?exchange=TW&lang=zh_TW',\n    ]\n    codes = set()\n    for url in urls:\n        try:\n            req = urllib.request.Request(url, headers=headers)\n            resp = urllib.request.urlopen(req, context=ctx, timeout=8)\n            raw = json.loads(resp.read())\n            # Parse whatever format comes back\n            text = json.dumps(raw, ensure_ascii=False)\n            # Extract 4-6 digit numbers that look like stock codes\n            import re\n            found = re.findall(r'\"(\\d{4,6})\"', text)\n            codes.update([c for c in found if 1000 <= int(c) <= 99999])\n        except:\n            pass\n    return sorted(list(codes))[:600]\n\n# ========================\n# 工具：fetch US stock lists\n# ========================\ndef fetch_us_list(wiki_url, col='Symbol'):\n    \"\"\"從 Wikipedia 抓 US 指數成分股\"\"\"\n    try:\n        tables = pd.read_html(wiki_url)\n        syms = tables[0][col].dropna().tolist()\n        # Clean yfinance tickers (. -> - for ETFs like ARNC -> ARNC)\n        return [str(s).replace('.', '-') for s in syms if isinstance(s, str)]\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"  ⚠️ Failed to fetch from {wiki_url}: {e}\")\n        return []\n\n# ========================\n# Vega 信號\n# ========================\ndef vegas_signal(close: pd.Series, volume: pd.Series):\n    if len(close) < 200:\n        return None\n\n    ema12  = close.ewm(span=12,  adjust=False).mean()\n    ema144 = close.ewm(span=144, adjust=False).mean()\n    ema169 = close.ewm(span="},"partialJson":"{\"content\":\"\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nVegas Tunnel 掃描器 - 全市場版\\n台股 TWSE 500: FinMind(優先) / yfinance(備用)\\n美股 S&P500 / NASDAQ100 / SOX30: yfinance(即時)\\n\\n執行: python vegas_scan.py\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\nimport sys, os\\nsys.path.insert(0, r'C:\\\\Users\\\\USER\\\\AppData\\\\Local\\\\Programs\\\\Python\\\\Python312\\\\Lib\\\\site-packages')\\nsys.path.insert(0, os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(__file__)))\\n\\nimport yfinance as yf\\nfrom FinMind.data import DataLoader\\nimport pandas as pd\\nimport numpy as np\\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\\nimport warnings, ssl, json, urllib.request\\nwarnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\n\\n# ========================\\n# 參數\\n# ========================\\nMIN_SCORE = 3\\nBACKTEST_DAYS = 700\\n\\n# ========================\\n# 工具：fetch TWSE 股票清單\\n# ========================\\ndef fetch_twse_list():\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"從 TWSE API 取得上市股票代碼\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    ctx = ssl.create_default_context()\\n    ctx.check_hostname = False\\n    ctx.verify_mode = ssl.CERT_NONE\\n    headers = {'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0', 'Accept': 'application/json'}\\n\\n    # 嘗試多个端點\\n    urls = [\\n        'https://www.twse.com.tw/rwd/zh/afterTrading/MI_INDEX?date=&type=ALL&response=json',\\n        'https://www.twse.com.tw/rwd/zh/listed/search_result?exchange=TW&lang=zh_TW',\\n    ]\\n    codes = set()\\n    for url in urls:\\n        try:\\n            req = urllib.request.Request(url, headers=headers)\\n            resp = urllib.request.urlopen(req, context=ctx, timeout=8)\\n            raw = json.loads(resp.read())\\n            # Parse whatever format comes back\\n            text = json.dumps(raw, ensure_ascii=False)\\n            # Extract 4-6 digit numbers that look like stock codes\\n            import re\\n            found = re.findall(r'\\\"(\\\\d{4,6})\\\"', text)\\n            codes.update([c for c in found if 1000 <= int(c) <= 99999])\\n        except:\\n            pass\\n    return sorted(list(codes))[:600]\\n\\n# ========================\\n# 工具：fetch US stock lists\\n# ========================\\ndef fetch_us_list(wiki_url, col='Symbol'):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"從 Wikipedia 抓 US 指數成分股\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    try:\\n        tables = pd.read_html(wiki_url)\\n        syms = tables[0][col].dropna().tolist()\\n        # Clean yfinance tickers (. -> - for ETFs like ARNC -> ARNC)\\n        return [str(s).replace('.', '-') for s in syms if isinstance(s, str)]\\n    except Exception as e:\\n        print(f\\\"  ⚠️ Failed to fetch from {wiki_url}: {e}\\\")\\n        return []\\n\\n# ========================\\n# Vega 信號\\n# ========================\\ndef vegas_signal(close: pd.Series, volume: pd.Series):\\n    if len(close) < 200:\\n        return None\\n\\n    ema12  = close.ewm(span=12,  adjust=False).mean()\\n    ema144 = close.ewm(span=144, adjust=False).mean()\\n    ema169 = close.ewm(span=","index":1}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":79352,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79352,"cost":{"input":0.0238056,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0238056}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778492271635,"responseId":"0650d672992a61f9ffe1331eeacff316"}}
