{"type":"message","id":"cef257e1","parentId":"d95a3098","timestamp":"2026-05-11T09:59:00.379Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Everything works. Now let me summarize the status and offer to run the full scan.\n","thinkingSignature":"33e153592697ef23779b0dc25f4be9e3a63d6385624c4a8cb5f8b83b9abb45dd"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ **vegas_scan.py 完成**，實測全部正常：\n\n---\n\n## 登入驗證結果\n\n| 項目 | 狀態 |\n|------|------|\n| Shioaji 登入 | ✅ 成功（2個帳戶：周蘇瑋）|\n| 2330 Shioaji K棒 | ✅ 2235元、EMA144=1743、EMA169=1692、隧道多頭 |\n| FinMind 備用 | ✅ 正常 |\n| yfinance（US）| ✅ 正常 |\n| S&P500/NDX100/Wiki | ✅ 可抓取 |\n\n---\n\n## 最終資料來源架構\n\n```\nTWSE 600檔：Shioaji(永豐) → FinMind(備用) → yfinance(最後備用)\nS&P500 503檔：yfinance（即時）\nNASDAQ100 101檔：yfinance（即時）\nSOX30 30檔：yfinance（即時）\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 執行\n\n```bash\nC:\\Users\\USER\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python312\\python.exe vegas_scan.py\n```\n\n預估時間：\n- TWSE 600檔：5-10 分鐘（Shioaji 速度快）\n- US（S&P500 + NDX100 + SOX30）：8-12 分鐘\n- 合計約 **15-20 分鐘**\n\n要現在執行嗎？📈"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":521,"output":317,"cacheRead":103872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104710,"cost":{"input":0.0001563,"output":0.0003804,"cacheRead":0.0062323199999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00676902}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778493522099,"responseId":"0650db54dbbc65b40e2504b6b74a3ddf"}}
